headline: Is It Worth Investing in AT&T (T) Based on Wall Street's Bullish Views?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), AT&T (T) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: AT&T CEO: AI's power shortages could become America's "next economic social issue" - Fortune Global Forum
summary: AT&T CEO John Stankey told the Fortune Global Forum in 2024 that AI power shortages could be America’s next economic social issue. This year, the Fortune Global Forum will convene October 26–27 in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia, to explore the strategies that will define the next era of business growth.
